{"tid":1746293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消防處出新內部通告，稱可不用戴名牌","createTime":"2019-11-22T16:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T16:58:40.000Z","uid":20348,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f103bf74b3171819f87c57e35e81c4b7d1ab65","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91OBxf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91OBxf.jpg&h=ca7323c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係咁，大家都知香港人對消防救護一向信任同愛戴，就算佢被黑警徵用救護車都提大家如何分真假與急否。<br />\n<br />\n但係咁次出份咁嘅內部通知，擺明想拉埋前線消防救護落水。<br />\n第一，大家都會諗到黑警同老解隨時可以笠件衫就扮消防救護。<br />\n<br />\n第二，咁做就根本地對傷者極不負責任，因為有假扮嘅嫌疑，開路就會令到救人時間拉長，從而令到對家有野做我地話示威者阻礙救援工作，touch wood死人黑警都話唔關我地事。<br />\n<br />\n第三，對上白車者，極無人身安全嘅保障，我點知自己上左架真白車定假白車。<br />\n<br />\n如果前線救護員見到，請你地堅守原則與救護守則，請不要與黑警同流合污，以免蒙上不白之冤。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察，我屌你老母臭系。<br />\n消防高層，我屌你老母臭系十次。</span><br />\n<br />\n圖片出處：林鴻達fb"},{"pid":"09a1787c1773f0587a8b33312737cfc4e7974899","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2e09a62128664c8019670e081769860d8cc7071c","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"2推！"},{"pid":"a02eecace8438ba9bfe6f2cdfb721f164b52e694","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:23:50.000Z","msg":"3推！"},{"pid":"017f2d5de3ed5e8ab05697c51385a86ead41911a","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"4推！"},{"pid":"b1bad62e6afe0989efbdd88b5ec1744c2cebc97a","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"5推！"},{"pid":"560f0f8cf2567ac06dab006a7038e9b8c2728cb0","tid":1746293,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:24:24.00